Handles Native Image unsupported dynamic class loading by verifying `NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(...)`.\n\nPer your instruction, I did not compile or run the tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_04012b1346cd859e0169f6537e6d9881948aa82b2589ea880d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 482, "output": 1177, "cacheRead": 52224, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 53883, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777750897363, "responseId": "resp_04012b1346cd859e0169f65371f0948194a1aac554731a9d87"}, "toolResults": []}
